{
  "chapter": 47,
  "chapter_summary": "第四十七回\"找的不是你\"主要讲述小方和阳光寻找卜鹰的过程中遇到神秘歌者。歌者透露卜鹰已不愿再见他们，并归还阳光亲手缝制的订亲锦囊和明珠，锦囊和明珠落入火中焚毁。歌者声称卜鹰认为小方已不是朋友，小方理解这是卜鹰为保护他们而故意疏远。歌者随后自尽以保守卜鹰下落。赵群约小方到山坡，透露有重大秘密要告知，但此时苏苏的惊呼打断了对话。小方和赵群赶回石屋，发现阳光被五人掳走，苏苏被侵害。赵群和小方分头追寻阳光未果。小方回到石屋，发现一个吕三属下正在侵害苏苏，小方愤怒将其打死。苏苏被灌下销魂胭脂酒后与小方发生关系。苏苏醒来后告诉小方那是吕三属下的所为，吕三手下已能认出她，催促小方离开。小方决定带苏苏一起走，去找吕三。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "歌者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不是他，是我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "歌者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们要找的是他，不是我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_ge_zhe",
      "text": "你知道我们要找的是他不是你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_ge_zhe",
      "text": "你怎么知道的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "歌者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_ge_zhe",
      "text": "你也知道他是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "歌者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我知道。我当然知道他是谁。我到这里来，就是他要我来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_ge_zhe",
      "text": "他要你来干什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "歌者",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "你还记不记得这是什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "歌者",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "这是他交给我的。亲手交给我的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 49
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_ge_zhe",
      "text": "他为什么要交给你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "歌者",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "因为他要我替他把这样东西还给你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "歌者",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "他说他本来应该亲手还给你的，但是他已不愿再见你。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_ge_zhe",
      "text": "他说他不愿见她，真是他说的？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "歌者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他还说了另外一句话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_ge_zhe",
      "text": "什么话？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "歌者",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "他说他也不愿再见你。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "歌者",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你已经不是他的朋友。从此以后，他和你们之间已完全没有关系。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_ge_zhe",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "歌者",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你自己应该知道为什么。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "歌者",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你自己愿不愿意跟一个天天抱住你妻子睡觉的人交朋友？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_ge_zhe",
      "text": "我不信，我死也不信他会说出这样的话。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_ge_zhe",
      "text": "一定是你杀了他，再用这种话来欺骗我。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "歌者",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "我为什么要骗你？如果不是他告诉我的，你们的事我怎么会知道？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_ge_zhe",
      "text": "不管怎么样，我一定要听他自己亲口告诉我，我才相信。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_ge_zhe",
      "text": "你一定知道他在哪里，一定要告诉我。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "歌者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，我告诉你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "歌者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "虽然我不能告诉你他在什么地方，但我却可以告诉你一件事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "歌者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "十三年前，我就已经应该死了，死得很惨。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "歌者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我还没有死，只因为卜鹰救了我。不但救了我的命，也救了我的名声。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "歌者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以我这条命已经是他的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "歌者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以我随时都可以为他死。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "歌者",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我早就知道你们一定会逼我说出他的下落。除了你们之外，一定还有很多人会逼我，幸好我也已经有法子让你们逼不出来。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_ge_zhe",
      "text": "我相信你的话，我绝不逼你！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "赵群",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我知道卜鹰这个人，我见过他一次。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "赵群",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "千古艰难惟一死。要一个人心甘情愿的为另一个人死去，绝不是件容易事。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "赵群",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "卜鹰的确不愧为人杰。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "赵群",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "但是不管多么了不起的人，也有做错事的时候。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "赵群",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我知道这次他一定冤枉了你。我看得出你跟那位姑娘都绝不是他说的那种人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_zhao_qun",
      "text": "他没有错，错的是你。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "赵群",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "是我？我错在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_zhao_qun",
      "text": "错在你根本不了解他。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这世界上本来就很少有人能了解他。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "赵群",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你好像一点都不恨他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_zhao_qun",
      "text": "我恨他？我为什么要恨他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_zhao_qun",
      "text": "难道你真的以为他是在怀疑我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_zhao_qun",
      "text": "难道他不是？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_zhao_qun",
      "text": "当然不是。他这么样做，只不过因不愿再连累我们，所以才故意刺伤我们，要我们永远不想再见他。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他这么做，只不过要我们自由自在的去过我们自己的日子。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "赵群",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你确实了解他。一个人能有你这么一个知己朋友，已经可以死而无憾了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "赵群",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "有些事我本来不想对你说的，可是现在也不能不说了。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_zhao_qun",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "赵群",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "是个秘密，到现在还没有人知道的秘密。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "赵群",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "如果不是因为这件事，我也永远不会告诉你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_zhao_qun",
      "text": "现在你是不是一定要说？我是不是一定要听？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "赵群",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么你说，我听。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "赵群",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "苏苏。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "赵群",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "什么事？谁欺负了你？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "阳光呢？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "五个人。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "赵群",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "追！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qun",
      "speaker_name": "赵群",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你往东追，我往西。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "这不能怪你。他逼我喝的是销魂胭脂酒，吕三也不知用这种酒毁掉了多少个女孩子的清白。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 500,
      "line_end": 504
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "吕三？那个人也是吕三的属下？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 506,
      "line_end": 508
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "他也是那五个人其中之一？阳光就是被他们掳走的？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 520,
      "line_end": 522
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我始终不明白，他们为什么要绑走她？却没有绑走我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 524,
      "line_end": 526
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "也许他们又把她当做了我？也许他们要找的本来就是她？反正吕三所做的事，总是让人摸不透的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 528,
      "line_end": 530
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "现在你是不是要走了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 534,
      "line_end": 534
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "如果你真的要走，要去找吕三，你用不着顾忌我。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 538,
      "line_end": 538
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我们本来就不算什么，你要走，随时都可以走。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 542,
      "line_end": 542
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "不管你能不能找到吕三，你都一定要走，非走不可。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 548,
      "line_end": 550
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 552,
      "line_end": 552
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "因为现在吕三手下已经有很多人都能认得出我了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 554,
      "line_end": 554
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "所以你一定要离开我。不管怎么样，我都不愿连累你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 558,
      "line_end": 560
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "我们一起走。你带我去找吕三，你一定能找得到他。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 566,
      "line_end": 568
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "能找到他又怎么样？去送死？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 570,
      "line_end": 572
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你知不知道吕三属下有多少高手？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 574,
      "line_end": 574
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我们走吧，现在就走。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 580,
      "line_end": 580
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_su_su",
      "text": "走？走到哪里去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 582,
      "line_end": 584
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "随便到哪里去。我们可以去找个没有人能找得到的地方躲起来。忘记所有的人，所有的事。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 586,
      "line_end": 590
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我知道你一定想问我，是不是也能忘记赵群？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 594,
      "line_end": 594
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_su",
      "speaker_name": "苏苏",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你以为我现在还有脸见赵群？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 596,
      "line_end": 596
    }
